name: Paper Wireframe Kit
description:
Figma Community Awards 2022 🗳 ✨

Paper Kit is a Finalist for the Figma Community Awards!! If you'd like to show your support, voting ends May 10! Thanks to everyone who's used Paper Kit, we truly appreciate your support 🥰


Made with ❤️ by Tyler Sharpe and Claire Lorman 🌈


About Paper Kit

Jump into your next project and generate concepts quickly with this Low-Fi wireframing kit.


Inspired by the analog process of paper prototyping, each component has been crafted to take a backseat to the overall experience you're aiming to create.


As Method's first published resource on Community, we're excited to see what you'll do with this simple kit. Created by both designers and strategists in-house, Paper Kit will help you zoom out, work quickly, and collaborate more effectively with your cohorts ✨


About Method


Method is a diverse team of strategists, designers, and engineers.


We believe that good technology improves our daily lives in ways that few things can. We exist to inspire and enable those wanting to create exceptional software and digital experiences. 👉Follow us on Figma Community!
